node.text: Hey Guys!! Just a heads up - thought I’d do a wee Instagram Live tomorrow July 23rd around 3pm PT - just to give back a little love that y’all have been sending our way lately with the success of #virginriver. Hopefully I can chat with some of you then ❤️🙏🏻

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Martin Henderson on July 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text: For all of you Virgin River fans in the US who’ve binged Season 3 already and wanna watch me be really nervous in a live interview talking about the show tune in to the Today show on CBS at 2pm E, 1pm central and 2pm PT TODAY

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Martin Henderson on July 10, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'Top 10 in the U.S. Today N VIRGIN RIVER 1 NEW EPISODES 2 MANIFES Watch It Again'.

node.text:
Woohoooo!!!! Can hardly believe it. So humbled by our little show’s success and so so grateful for every single one of you tuning in and supporting us 🙏🏻❤️ feels surreal but really nice to know you are so passionate about what our whole cast and crew work so hard to create!
😘😀
